  "texts": [
    "Among the 4C metrics, we observed that EchoGPT significantly outperformed human experts in conciseness (p<0.001).",
    "There was no significant difference among the other three categories (Figure 5A).",
    "The 4C metrics were not completely independent.",
    "There was a high correlation between clinical utility and completeness (Pearson's r= 0.78), and modest to moderate correlations between other metrics (Figure 5B).",
    "We also observed that across all automatic metrics, RadGraph F1 had modest to moderate correlations with all 4 human evaluation metrics (Figure 5C)."
